Package it.polimi.ingsw.controller

Interface CommandInterpreter

All Known Implementing Classes:
InitialisingInterpreter, LoginInterpreter, TurnsInterpreter
public interface CommandInterpreter
this class is used to execute commands, and create the response to the clients

  • Method Summary

    Modifier and Type Method Description
    ResponseToClient executeCommand​(Command command, ClientHandler client)
    this method execute the command given in input, returning a code that will be sent to the client associated with the handler the method will change the internal model state depending on the dynamic type of the commandInterpreter
    default CardColor getColor()
    this method get the color of the card that the player want to buy during the buy_card normal action in particular, get the right level when the interface is implemented by the class TurnsInterpreter, return null otherwise
    default int getDashboardPosition()
    this method get the position in which the player want to place the card that want to buy during the buy_card normal action in particular, get the right position when the interface is implemented by the class TurnsInterpreter, return 0 otherwise
    default int getFirstLeaderCard()
    this method get the index relative to the first card that the player want to discard during the initialising game phase.
    GamePhase getGamePhase()
    this method return the enum associated with the phase of the game for loginInterpreter, it returns LOGIN, for initialisingInterpreter, it returns INITIALISING, for turnsInterpreter, it returns TURNS
    default int getLevel()
    this method get the level of the card that the player want to buy during the buy_card normal action in particular, get the right level when the interface is implemented by the class TurnsInterpreter, return 0 otherwise
    default java.util.List<Marble> getMarbles()
    this method get the marbles that the player got in the market during the choose_marbles action.
    default CollectionResources getMarblesConverted()
    this method get the collectionResources associated with the marbles chosen from the market that have being converted into resources in particular, get the right resources when the interface is implemented by the class TurnsInterpreter, null otherwise

    this method get the possible command for a player according with the rules of the game
